## What Gets You Where

Different tiers of the leveling system correspond to different kinds of players.

- **Level 1–50** — social tasks plus light trading. Anyone who shows up gets here.
- **Level 50–100** — daily + seasonal trading quests become the dominant source.
- **Level 100–150** — requires consistent trading focus across multiple seasonal milestones.
- **Level 150–200** — heavy trading volume plus meaningful referral progress.
- **Level 200–250** — every trading quest cleared plus a deep referral tree.
- **Level 250–300** — maxing everything, repeatedly. Daily grind, every seasonal quest, every referral tier, plus repeatable social engagement. True endgame.

