## Points & The Moonsheet

Credits are one half of the equation. **Points** are the other.

Points are earned from your trading volume and the fees that volume generates. They're the direct measure of how much economic activity you've contributed to Interstate, and they're what determines your allocation when the Moonsheet drops.

### Volume-to-Points Conversion

- Every **$100 in trading volume → 1 Point-equivalent base unit**
- **20 Points per verified referred user**, 1 Point per unverified referred user
- **0.10% kickback** on all referred volume once your referrals cross $100K total
- Fees generated count directly toward your Points total

### Moonsheet Allocation

The Moonsheet is a **10% airdrop pool** denominated against the $INTR token's fully diluted valuation at launch.

| Launch FDV | Moonsheet Pool |
| ---------: | -------------: |
|       $50M |            $5M |
|      $100M |           $10M |
|      $200M |           $25M |
|      $500M |           $50M |

Your final allocation is your share of the total Points pool, applied against the Moonsheet size at launch. More Points, more tokens. Simple as that.

